{"tid":595784,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"幫人係街搵返隻狗 反被狗主控勒索","createTime":"2018-03-17T04:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T11:03:00.000Z","uid":24909,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e0f3b7164a37f61de48b9ba3d91ae3c78936174a","tid":595784,"uid":24909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T04:15:29.000Z","msg":"事緣係附近見到街招話尋狗<br />\n張街招就話搵返有酬勞,幾錢就唔講喇,都係兩三千左右<br />\n咁啱跑步見到路邊有隻狗行黎行去<br />\n留意左一陣都無主人係附近就截住左佢<br />\n見佢又唔怕人咁應該有人養架啦<br />\n咁順手就打電話畀狗主睇下係咪失狗<br />\n點不知狗主黎到多謝都無句聲<br />\n就大大聲話我偷左佢隻狗黎勒索佢地攞錢<br />\n係香港係咪真係咁難做好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5768cafb306ac88a70ff07c0ff3f9512b50ca3c","tid":595784,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T04:17:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e78f7855037796fff02e0ffb047dec36e204d3af","tid":595784,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"好慘<br />\n做好人死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n來生不做好人"},{"pid":"4218330786ed3434bd031309208919351d198048","tid":595784,"uid":86893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:50:37.000Z","msg":"三六滾一滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4484d75bbc1dcbfddb942cf84a607b8ee60d62b","tid":595784,"uid":130635,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:51:39.000Z","msg":"樓主你其實可以影低個街招，然後去小額錢債處告佢違約"},{"pid":"306b3e4ca821e134ddda6764eb68a5290deb9f02","tid":595784,"uid":91631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:52:47.000Z","msg":"咪唔還俾佢囉"},{"pid":"316e116ed317eb5a2dd4f3c93ca2635636455997","tid":595784,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4484d75bbc1dcbfddb942cf84a607b8ee60d62b","tid":595784,"uid":130635,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:51:39.000Z","msg":"樓主你其實可以影低個街招，然後去小額錢債處告佢違約"},"citedBy":0